{"tid":657050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文化衝擊]以色列為安倍提供甜品卻惹怒了安倍妻子","createTime":"2018-05-07T18:32:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T00:41:04.000Z","uid":41818,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"4555444e63f4ca7ec65f64492666d59f35e8c605","tid":657050,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:32:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/3507712037/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F3507712037%2F0&h=bb2defa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自從4月份，日本首相安倍攜妻子訪問美國，沒成想妻子貪杯差點喝醉之後，安倍再次遭遇尷尬一幕。<br />\n<br />\n日前，安倍攜妻子與以色列總理夫婦進餐的時候，以色列名廚為他的妻子準備的甜點，是放在一隻鞋子里，而他的妻子則因這種冒犯性的文化失禮而被迫停止進餐。<br />\n<br />\n對於任何一種文化來說，沒有哪種文化是把鞋子放在桌子上。無論如何，從鞋子里盛食物都是一種奇怪的現象，尤其是在日本，更是一種難以形容的、令人很不愉快的行為。<br />\n<br />\n以色列駐日本的高級外交官說：「這個做法，簡直是愚蠢、麻木、足夠侮辱的動作。」<br />\n<br />\n那麼為什麼他這麼說呢？<br />\n<br />\n對於了解日本文化的人來說，沒有什麼比鞋子更讓人鄙視的了。日本人不僅從不穿鞋進入自己的房間，而且在他們的辦公室也找不到鞋子。就連首相、部長和國會議員都不穿鞋上班。<br />\n<br />\n以色列廚子的做法，就相當於在一個形狀像豬的盤子里，為猶太客人提供巧克力。<br />\n<img src=\"http://i1.wp.com/inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/3507712040/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Finews.gtimg.com%2Fnewsapp_match%2F0%2F3507712040%2F0&h=638fe195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ifuun.com/a2018050812812784/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ifuun.com%2Fa2018050812812784%2F&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=cb28451c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ifuun.com/a2018050812812784/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.businessinsider.com/israel-served-japan-prime-minister-shinzo-abe-dessert-out-of-a-shoe-2018-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-served-japan-prime-minister-shinzo-abe-dessert-out-of-a-shoe-2018-5&d=ltR1ESwHDkZv1QxYodHvaW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a88ad34a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.businessinsider.com/israel-served-japan-prime-minister-shinzo-abe-dessert-out-of-a-shoe-2018-5</a>"},{"pid":"e9e1128d33ea9e06c963da39ebd1b9b225bc6e48","tid":657050,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:34:54.000Z","msg":"里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487420753f2192d44f969dcf0ef9b1f528356ce0","tid":657050,"uid":123264,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:46:16.000Z","msg":"垃圾女人 食你就食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b73b8a4a9cfc846c39fccd55584b024d16ab5c","tid":657050,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:50:53.000Z","msg":"歐洲支那，亡國啦"},{"pid":"2ab1d8f39024e68056194d546b4b0db7de62a0e0","tid":657050,"uid":96743,"like":35,"dislike":4,"score":31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T18:59:15.000Z","msg":"又真係會嬲<br />\n屌你老母全部人都正常得佢份係咁<br />\n唔嬲就假"},{"pid":"24a9937571646e0c72393e7e4462bc5b7816bb0b","tid":657050,"uid":44454,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"個廚師都低能，唔好話文唔文化，鞋本身就俾人又臭又污糟嘅感覺，根本大部份人都食唔落口"},{"pid":"6b68a1b1691edf4b9ae194fb59e224a097dc3b84","tid":657050,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"24a9937571646e0c72393e7e4462bc5b7816bb0b","tid":657050,"uid":44454,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"個廚師都低能，唔好話文唔文化，鞋本身就俾人又臭又污糟嘅感覺，根本大部份人都食唔落口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T19:02:36.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔識欣賞"},{"pid":"608fe1096421f6f3bd8210b2dea461d8984bf538","tid":657050,"uid":162535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"01b73b8a4a9cfc846c39fccd55584b024d16ab5c","tid":657050,"uid":54876,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T